WEBVTT


00:00:00.356 --> 00:00:01.515
A part of the cross

00:00:01.516 --> 00:00:04.395
that Jesus Christ is believed to have been crucified on

00:00:04.396 --> 00:00:06.143
has been given to King Charles.

00:00:06.236 --> 00:00:08.623
2 shards of the cross will be used in his coronation

00:00:08.716 --> 00:00:10.903
and incorporated into the cross of Wales.

00:00:11.160 --> 00:00:11.735
Both pieces,

00:00:11.736 --> 00:00:14.243
which are 1cm and 5mm,

00:00:14.336 --> 00:00:16.655
are set into the larger silver cross

00:00:16.656 --> 00:00:18.415
behind a crystal gemstone.

00:00:18.416 --> 00:00:20.883
They've been gifted to the king by the Pope.
